List available WFS layers

listLayers.Rd

Lists layers available from Vicmap

listLayers(...)

Arguments

...

Additional arguments passed to str_detect. The pattern argument can be used to search for specific layers with matching names or titles.

Value

data.frame

Examples

listLayers(pattern = stringr::regex("flood height contour", ignore_case = TRUE))
#>                             Name
#> 1  datavic:FLOOD_CONTOUR_20Y_ARI
#> 2  datavic:FLOOD_CONTOUR_50Y_ARI
#> 3  datavic:FLOOD_CONTOUR_10Y_ARI
#> 4 datavic:FLOOD_CONTOUR_100Y_ARI
#> 5 datavic:FLOOD_CONTOUR_200Y_ARI
#> 6   datavic:FLOOD_CONTOUR_5Y_ARI
#> 7 datavic:FLOOD_CONTOUR_500Y_ARI
#>                                                       Title
#> 1    Victoria Flood Database - Flood Height Contour 20 year
#> 2    Victoria Flood Database - Flood Height Contour 50 year
#> 3   Victoria Flood Database - Flood Height Contours 10 year
#> 4 Victoria Flood Database - Flood Height Contours 100  year
#> 5  Victoria Flood Database - Flood Height Contours 200 year
#> 6    Victoria Flood Database - Flood Height Contours 5 year
#> 7 Victoria Flood Database - Flood Height Contours 500 years
